Text: Hi there can i import this into mapsource and  edit it becoz i didnt need Svalbard  etc  only  need around denmark westcoast.Thanks

No you can´t. Garmin BlueChart G2 is only sold on SD cards, not as mapsource installs.

So it´s all or nothing, but a SD card is cheap :)
I can use it on my  GPSMAP 60 SX ,i  used a 2 gb  microcard  made a directory  Garmin  put it in and  it booted like sh..   Thankyou  for  sharing

Is it possible to get a guide on how to install this?
Many years since i used torrents and cracks.

just drag GMAPSUPP.IMG and drop it on gimgunlock.exe, a command prompt opens and the GMAPSUPP.IMG is unlocked in seconds.

copy GMAPSUPP.IMG to a folder named Garmin on your SD card.

Done
